# AI Agent Rules

## Tech Stack
- **Styling**: Always use [TailwindCSS](https://tailwindcss.com/) for styling.
- **Components**: Always use [shadcn/ui](https://ui.shadcn.com/) components.

## React Patterns
- **Client Components**: Only use `"use client"` when it's important. Do not use it by default.

## Design System
- **Globals**: Always check `app/globals.css` for design tokens and variables before creating new styles.

## Package Management
- **Manager**: Always use `pnpm` as the package manager.